criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with confirmed multiple sclerosis by McDonald criteria;

          -  score 25 or less in mini mental state examination (MMSE)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  MMSE score greater than 25;

          -  the history of psychiatric problems;

          -  addiction to alcohol; head trauma; cerebrovascular disease; hydrocephalus; neoplasm;
             epilepsy; renal or respiratory diseases; impaired consciousness
